Package: cricketr
Type: Package
Title: The cricketr package can be used to analyze crickers based on ESPN
    Cricinfo Statsguru
Description: This package analyzes performances of cricketers based on stats in
    ESPN Cricinfo Statsguru. The analyses can be done for Tests,ODIs and Twenty20
    for batsmen and bowlers.
Version: 0.0.9
Date: 2015-12-26
Author: Tinniam V Ganesh
Maintainer: Tinniam V Ganesh <tvganesh.85@gmail.com>
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    plotrix,
    ggplot2,
    scatterplot3d,
    forecast,
    lubridate,
    XML
URL: https://github.com/tvganesh/cricketr
BugReports: https://github.com/tvganesh/cricketr/issues
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
